I would try to find somewhere less... risky, like the inside of a library book, and make the art loosely relevant to the book.', 'love the idea, but where i live i would risk a fine for littering', "@keii4ii I know right? I thought about someone tossing it too. But I do a lot of things without guarantee of results with art. Just thinks it's pretty cool to give it a try.Wouldn't spend too much on the drawing just in case!
