Last year I tapped the drawing under one of the mushrooms of the Alice In Wonderland sculpture.
Oh yeah, all these places are in NYC lol", "Oh cool! Thought I'd be all by myself on this one!I Just have to figure out what I'll draw.Maybe something original for the occasion.
I know I'll end up using an old drawing from my sketchbook if I lack time...Just have to be beautiful for someone to pick it up!"]

