Tapastic Winter Fest 2015 Dec 2 :: End. by9 @talissacosta1

 9It's a new day which means a new holiday collab comic over on Talissa's series, End.4
Check out her beautiful episode and see if you can spot all the cameos and hidden Tapastic Mascots. There are so many great hidden Easter Eggs in her episode. Also while you're visiting her series, why not give the rest of her comic a good read and show her some love. <3
